{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Post-1fa8 corrections: the g2p config artifact is infra/gerrit/gerrit_to_platform.ini.template rendered by materialize-g2p-config.sh (SSM PAT substitution at container boot) — record the verified branch-filter statement against the TEMPLATE + g2p source. Template today has NO branch-filter key (mapping recheck=verify + token only) — supports the no-op hypothesis. gerrit-verify.yaml is real: GERRIT_REFSPEC input, checkout-gerrit-change-action@v1.0.2, concurrency group gerrit-verify-CHANGE_ID cancel-in-progress. NOTE: Verified submit-requirement is authored INACTIVE (applicableIf=is:false) pending 1fa8's live flip — Verified VOTING re-runs regardless, but BLOCKING behavior needs the flip."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782980211510942001,"uuid":"46a7f94e-b898-4676-8fe0-b68f4dad5a8e"}